subject: Olympic Games (2012)
Marathon Running
Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Haile Gebrselassie, the former world-record holder in the 10,000 meters, failed to qualify Sunday for the event at the London Games, finishing seventh at the FBK Games in Hengelo, the Netherlands.
